00:19:30.530 --> 00:19:31.380
Vâng.

00:19:31.950 --> 00:19:32.670
Mời ngồi.

00:19:34.900 --> 00:19:35.720
Tại sao?

00:19:37.270 --> 00:19:38.220
Ôi cha!

00:19:42.190 --> 00:19:43.230
Anh biết mà.

00:19:43.600 --> 00:19:45.710
Maika to gan thật đó.

00:19:49.780 --> 00:19:51.190
Em đói rồi.

00:19:51.960 --> 00:19:53.610
